<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The documentation for <a href="http://framework.zend.com/manual/en/zend.application.available-resources.html#zend.application.available-resources.layout">Zend_Application_Resource_Layout</a> shows the below example</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
resources.layout.Path = "/path/to/layouts"
</code></pre>

<p>The "Path" key is incorrect and should be "layoutPath" as per the <a href="http://framework.zend.com/manual/en/zend.layout.options.html">Zend_Layout options</a>.</p>

